WEBVTT
1
00:00:01.930 --> 00:00:07.150
In this course, you will learn everything you need to know to start building your own extensions for

2
00:00:07.150 --> 00:00:08.080
web browsers.

3
00:00:08.350 --> 00:00:14.440
We will start by introducing you to the basics of extension development, including the tools and technologies.

4
00:00:14.620 --> 00:00:20.800
I will explain all the concepts that are essential to get you started in all four levels.

5
00:00:21.190 --> 00:00:28.540
You will learn about the session Essential Concepts Chromebase and then the advanced functionalities.

6
00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:34.150
I will teach you how to publish your chrome extensions and how to convert those Chrome extensions to

7
00:00:34.150 --> 00:00:35.650
Firefox extensions.

8
00:00:36.370 --> 00:00:42.910
We will delve into the process of building an extension, covering topics such as user interface design,

9
00:00:42.910 --> 00:00:47.320
modifying the web page, DOM data storage and working with APIs.

10
00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:52.600
You will learn how to debug and troubleshoot your extension and how to publish it to the store.

11
00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:56.110
We will build four extensions, one for each level.

12
00:00:57.130 --> 00:01:03.130
Along the way you will have the opportunity to put your skills to use by building a series of increasingly

13
00:01:03.130 --> 00:01:04.450
complex extensions.

14
00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:09.430
By the end of this course, you will have the knowledge and skills you need to start building your own

15
00:01:09.430 --> 00:01:10.210
extensions.

16
00:01:10.660 --> 00:01:15.370
So if you're ready to dive into the world of extension development, let's get started.
